<div class="title">First Time Use Induces Seizure</div>
<div class="substance">2C-B</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=collegekid&Exact=1">collegekid</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; collegekid. "First Time Use Induces Seizure: An Experience with 2C-B (exp103729)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Nov 14, 2014. erowid.org/exp/103729</div>

<br/>



